high_descs: Turn around, turn right, go straight toward the oven.
Pick up the left most pot on the stove.
Turn around, go straight, then turn right at the fridge.
Chill the pot in the fridge.
Turn around, move forward, then turn left to approach the oven.
Put the pot on the stove in the left front corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the fridge, then turn right and walk across the room to the oven.
Pick up the leftmost large metal pot on the stove.
Turn around and walk across the room to the fridge.

Open the fridge doors and place the large metal pot inside to the right of the glass, then close the fridge doors, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up, remove the large metal pot, then close the fridge.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk across the room to the stove.
Place the large metal pot back on the stove on the front left burner.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled metal pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the stove.
Pick up the pan on the left side of the stove.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Put the pan inside the refrigerator.
Take the pan out of the refrigerator.
Turn to the right, go to the stove and put the pan on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Chill the pan in the refrigerator.
